Requirements

None (only the 'GeoIP.dat' file is needed).  To download a free March 2002
database, go to
http://maxmind.com/download/geoip/database/

Install

Just place the 'geoip.inc.php' file somewhere according to the 'include_path' directive of
your 'php.ini' file.
Edit the 'geoip.inc.php' file and change the value of the  'GeoIP_DATADIR' constant in
order to match the location of your 'GeoIP.dat' file.

Usage

Gets country name by hostname :

require('geoip.inc.php');

$my_geoip = new GeoIP();
echo $my_geoip->Country_name_by_name("amazon.com");
